==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Shield-bearer
<hw>Shield"-bear`er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>One who, or that which, carries a shield.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Any small moth of the genus
<gen>Aspidisca</gen>, whose larva makes a shieldlike covering for itself
out of bits of leaves.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Shielddrake</ent>⟦br⟧
